{"tid":2243968,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"辱華風波發酵 內地廣告下架 國際Fans圍中  BTS未驚過 反追究中國影音平台侵權","createTime":"2020-10-15T06:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T02:13:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2c6178f775c40d4e60fac0b5af1f33436b9e59","tid":2243968,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201015/C7LDKDRGURGBZNPVFC56NWGDDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201015%2FC7LDKDRGURGBZNPVFC56NWGDDE%2F&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyif7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=483ae4d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201015%2FC7LDKDRGURGBZNPVFC56NWGDDE%2F&h=9cc140ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201015/C7LDKDRGURGBZNPVFC56NWGDDE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n辱華風波發酵 內地廣告下架 國際Fans圍中 <br />\nBTS未驚過 反追究中國影音平台侵權<br />\n<br />\n紅爆全球的韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS），在各地擁有大量ARMY（BTS歌迷稱呼），上周他們獲頒表揚促進韓美關係的獎項，成員RM發表得獎感言時因提及韓戰，誰料觸怒內地小粉紅的玻璃心，批評其感言涉嫌辱華。事件連日不斷發酵，近日由BTS代言的多個品牌廣告於內地網站及社交平台先後下架。不過，BTS則獲其他國家ARMY力撐，難怪他們所屬Big Hit事務所「未驚過」，更打算追究內地影音平台涉上載BTS演唱會的侵權行為，力爭到底。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【誤踩地雷】韓星言行 易觸發小粉紅神經<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mjoowory9x3Hor_R6jhQ6l_giRQ=/1280x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VLKSVMBBKREUVKB4M26WJ3WFRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmjoowory9x3Hor_R6jhQ6l_giRQ%3D%2F1280x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVLKSVMBBKREUVKB4M26WJ3WFRE.jpg&h=70a71bc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■韓國男團BTS近日關於韓戰的言論被指涉辱華，觸動內地小粉紅的玻璃心，叫他們「滾出中國」。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n韓男團BTS上周三（7日）獲得由The Korea Society主辦的「James A. Van Fleet Award」，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-RQ4K-NDeO1-Hg5Lb4TVSk55Tv8=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NFBFDCVSHBE6ZEL6YYYAA52W44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-RQ4K-NDeO1-Hg5Lb4TVSk55Tv8%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNFBFDCVSHBE6ZEL6YYYAA52W44.jpg&h=1038e8e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■韓男團BTS獲得James A. Van Fleet Award，隊長RM於得獎感言感謝美國，卻被內地小粉紅斥責不尊重韓戰中犧牲的中國人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WsE0CiMGvdF_M0FZycXe8sS7cIs=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/USWA2ZY4OZBZLNMYAYBB2F4ZDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWsE0CiMGvdF_M0FZycXe8sS7cIs%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUSWA2ZY4OZBZLNMYAYBB2F4ZDE.jpg&h=f1b0f2d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■BTS日前舉行的網上演唱會全球有近百萬人觀看直播，卻被內地影音網站侵權擺上架，難怪BTS經理人打算提告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XSbiBSAR1Hi8_ee_y3o-0MaeyAk=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJLBY5BZ35DZXJUMG3A5M7Z5CI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXSbiBSAR1Hi8_ee_y3o-0MaeyAk%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJLBY5BZ35DZXJUMG3A5M7Z5CI.jpg&h=04ca127d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■由BTS所代言的手機等廣告，紛紛於內地被下架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中韓外交部罕有回應欲降溫<br />\n<br />\n連日來事件不停發酵，近日由BTS代言的韓國品牌三星、現代汽車以及運動品牌FILA，相繼把他們的廣告於內地網站下架，內地網民隨即讚好：「BTS損失。。。。。。。。。。。。。。未有辱華意思。內地官媒《環球時報》昨早報道BTS事件時，指出有韓媒抨擊內地網民反應過度；甚至是「過激的愛國主義表現」等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【韓戰三年】死傷失蹤至少200萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PYc_cqH3sWR-vI-WkDM1khEnuOE=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3FL2FRC5JCGHKJCNMOJGJ3Q5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPYc_cqH3sWR-vI-WkDM1khEnuOE%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3FL2FRC5JCGHKJCNMOJGJ3Q5I.jpg&h=eabc0439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■BTS罕有地引來中韓兩邊的外交部回應，中方發言人趙立堅更說要「珍愛和平、促進友好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QzrHK9UNZY_amfL7g_AgJ71Q_HQ=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QXI6XKMW6NFFXKOLBFDWZ3R45Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQzrHK9UNZY_amfL7g_AgJ71Q_HQ%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQXI6XKMW6NFFXKOLBFDWZ3R45Y.jpg&h=6994950c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃之鋒昨日於twitter力撐BTS，直言應發展多元化市場，避免將所有資源投放屢屢用政治凌駕經濟的中國。 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：民族主義令人擔憂<br />\n<br />\n事件似乎未有影響BTS所屬事務所Big Hit今日在韓國上市的安排，曾有投資人擔心BTS風波會影響到Big Hit上市股價，但有分析卻指BTS已是世界級組合，多年來着重歐、美及東南亞等市場，未有太過依賴內地市場，相信沒大影響，而BTS近日亦繼《Dynamite》，BTS前日再以《Savage Love（Laxed &ndash; Siren Beat）》Remix版再奪美國Billboard Hot 100冠軍，足證人氣依舊爆燈。而Big Hit更似乎「未驚過」，據聞他們正打算採取行動追究內地影音平台Bilibili疑涉侵權行為，因網站非法上載BTS在上周六及本周日在首爾舉行的《Map of the Soul ON:E》演唱會，此兩日演唱會於網上直播，獲191個國家地區、吸引近100萬人收看。前日有報道指Big Hit接受媒體訪問時表示，近日BTS演唱會視頻在內地視頻網站上非法上載，稱內地嚴重侵犯韓國的文化信息著作權，還稱內地網友近日將BTS發表的感言指為政治言論，令人「哭笑不得」。<br />\n<br />\n另歐、美及亞洲等地BTS的ARMY亦集合起來守護偶像，引起反華情緒及聲言抵制，更有人用「Ugly Chinese」來形容內地網民，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。報道，似欲為事件降溫。"},{"pid":"8a793c8c18203c07a4555051af0f48cdec3a8d82","tid":2243968,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b0765eed96b153d6fd1d2c1c35af9e298e776e","tid":2243968,"uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\